#lang scribble/manual

@title{About Color}

You can set a color throuth 3 forms:

1. use name

   "red" "blue" "green"...

2. use 6 hex style: "#******"

   "#FFFFFF", "#FF0000"...

   hex style is case insensitive: "#ff00FF"

3. use 3 hex style: "#***"

   "#FFF" = "#FFFFFF"
   
   "#00F" = "#0000FF"

4. use rgb style: "rgb(xx, xx, xx)"

   "rgb(255, 255, 255)"